{
  "video_id": "3MHGl6WB_GM",
  "title": "California \"Shoplifting\" Laws - Penal Code 459.5 PC",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 6140.0,
      "end_time": 12350.0,
      "text": "Penal Code 459.5 defines the crime of shoplifting."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 12350.0,
      "end_time": 17509.0,
      "text": "Shoplifting is when you enter a store intending"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17510.0,
      "end_time": 20230.0,
      "text": "to steal merchandise inside."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20230.0,
      "end_time": 22180.0,
      "text": "And keep in mind, you don&#39;t even have"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22180.0,
      "end_time": 23980.0,
      "text": "to ultimately steal the merchandise."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23980.0,
      "end_time": 26220.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t even have to make it outside the store."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 26220.0,
      "end_time": 29880.0,
      "text": "Simply entering the store with the intent to steal"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 29880.0,
      "end_time": 31830.0,
      "text": "is enough to complete the crime."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 31830.0,
      "end_time": 34309.0,
      "text": "Now it used to be that entering a store intending"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34310.0,
      "end_time": 37770.0,
      "text": "to steal anything at all could be charged as burglary, which"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37770.0,
      "end_time": 40740.0,
      "text": "is a [? wobbler ?], which means it could be filed as a felony"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40740.0,
      "end_time": 44310.0,
      "text": "and carried up to three years in jail or prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44310.0,
      "end_time": 47250.0,
      "text": "But that changed under Proposition 47"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47250.0,
      "end_time": 49390.0,
      "text": "in November 2014."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49390.0,
      "end_time": 52200.0,
      "text": "So now, if you enter the store intending to steal--"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52200.0,
      "end_time": 55330.0,
      "text": "or actually do steal-- merchandise that&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 55330.0,
      "end_time": 60890.0,
      "text": "worth $950 or less, then it can only"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60900.0,
      "end_time": 63420.0,
      "text": "be charged as misdemeanor shoplifting."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63420.0,
      "end_time": 65840.0,
      "text": "If you enter intending to steal-- or do"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65840.0,
      "end_time": 70280.0,
      "text": "steal-- merchandise worth more than $950,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70280.0,
      "end_time": 72800.0,
      "text": "then it could be filed as felony burglary."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72800.0,
      "end_time": 76306.0,
      "text": "But the threshold is $950."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76306.0,
      "end_time": 78429.0,
      "text": "Now if you&#39;re convicted of misdemeanor shoplifting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78430.0,
      "end_time": 80700.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll likely be put on misdemeanor or summary"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 80700.0,
      "end_time": 83500.0,
      "text": "probation, you&#39;ll have to pay a fine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 83500.0,
      "end_time": 86400.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll be ordered to stay away from the location,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 86400.0,
      "end_time": 88590.0,
      "text": "and sometimes a judge will impose jail time."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 88590.0,
      "end_time": 91890.0,
      "text": "And the maximum sentence is up to year in county jail."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 91890.0,
      "end_time": 94490.0,
      "text": "Moreover, it looks really bad on your record."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 94490.0,
      "end_time": 97940.0,
      "text": "Nobody wants to be sitting in a job interview explaining"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 97940.0,
      "end_time": 99620.0,
      "text": "to a prospective employer why they&#39;ve"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 99620.0,
      "end_time": 101760.0,
      "text": "been convicted of shoplifting."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 101760.0,
      "end_time": 106400.0,
      "text": "So to the extent that you got cited or arrested or charged"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 106400.0,
      "end_time": 109970.0,
      "text": "with shoplifting under Penal Code 459.5,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 109970.0,
      "end_time": 113220.0,
      "text": "you want to do everything possible to fight the case"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 113220.0,
      "end_time": 114750.0,
      "text": "and keep it off you record."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 114750.0,
      "end_time": 116230.0,
      "text": "Here at Shouse Law Group, we&#39;ve had"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 116230.0,
      "end_time": 119460.0,
      "text": "a lot of success in defending clients in these cases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 119460.0,
      "end_time": 122929.0,
      "text": "and many times we find that it&#39;s a situation where our client"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 122930.0,
      "end_time": 124940.0,
      "text": "genuinely forgot to pay."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 124940.0,
      "end_time": 127320.0,
      "text": "We had a case recently at a department store,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 127320.0,
      "end_time": 130508.0,
      "text": "where our client had a bunch of merchandise"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 130508.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133590.0,
      "text": "in her shopping cart and she went up to check out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 133600.0,
      "end_time": 136920.0,
      "text": "she put it on the check stand, and there were a couple items"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 136920.0,
      "end_time": 138739.0,
      "text": "that she forgot to take out of the cart"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 138740.0,
      "end_time": 141100.0,
      "text": "and put on the check stand to pay for."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 141100.0,
      "end_time": 144200.0,
      "text": "She was distracted, she had a kid who was crying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 144200.0,
      "end_time": 146970.0,
      "text": "her cell phone was ringing-- she simply made a mistake"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 146970.0,
      "end_time": 150196.0,
      "text": "and forgot to put these extra items on the check stand."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 150196.0,
      "end_time": 151950.0,
      "text": "She walked out of the store without paying"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 151950.0,
      "end_time": 154700.0,
      "text": "for them, got apprehended by Loss Prevention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 154700.0,
      "end_time": 156660.0,
      "text": "arrested for shoplifting."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 156660.0,
